title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 329-1.1 - Applicability of schedule
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 329-1.1 - Applicability of schedule

State Regulations

The fee schedule applicable to medical, physical therapy
and occupational therapy services shall be the medical fee schedule in effect
on the date on which the medical, physical therapy or occupational therapy
services were rendered, regardless of the date of accident. Notes
